last_episode_to_air.overview: With Hillerska's fate hanging in the balance, Wilhelm and Simon weigh duty against love as they discover what it takes to truly follow their hearts.

name: Young Royals
overview: Prince Wilhelm adjusts to life at his prestigious new boarding school, Hillerska, but following his heart proves more challenging than anticipated.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: After a video of Prince Wilhelm of Sweden fighting at a party is posted online, he is given a script for an apology speech and learns that his parents have enrolled him at Hillerska Boarding School, a prestigious boarding school in the country.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: A winter break has passed and Prince Wilhelm and the rest of his classmates are back at Hillerska. When Wilhelm tries to take revenge on August, and win back Simon's trust, he creates problems that threaten the entire monarchy.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: The prince and Simon are determined to be together, but what are they willing to sacrifice when realizing that their freedom and love might be at odds with the Royal ideals, traditions, and responsibilities?

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Following a scandal, Prince Wilhelm enrolls in a new boarding school, Hillerska. His second cousin, August, plans an initiation party in his honor.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Simon and Wilhelm spend time together outside of school. Desperate for ADHD medication, August attempts to get diagnosed. Rowing tryouts commence.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Hillerska hosts a spirited Parents' Weekend but a bevy of surprises, disappointments and more occur for Wilhelm, August, Felice and Simon.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Wilhelm struggles with his grief and what the loss of his family member means for his future. Simon pressures August to repay him.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: August and Wilhelm face off over how to resolve a disciplinary problem at school. Sara revels in hanging out with Felice and her friends.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Wilhelm feels conflicted about how to handle the aftermath of the leaked video while Simon fends off the press. Felice makes a discovery.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: After a video of Prince Wilhelm of Sweden fighting at a party is posted online, he is given a script for an apology speech and learns that his parents have enrolled him at Hillerska Boarding School, a prestigious boarding school in the country.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Animosity lingers between Wilhelm and August as a new semester at Hillerska begins. Sara finally gets to experience campus life.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Negotiating the harsh consequences of his rebellion, Wilhelm presents the Queen with an ultimatum. Birthday celebrations remind Sara she's an outsider.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: A combative rowing competition gets even more heated due to Simon's surprise guest. Summoned by the Queen for a talk, August fears for his future.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Rumors about a girl in Wilhelm's room circulate while Sara's fling might be short-lived. The girls rebel against antiquated Valentine's Ball traditions.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Last-minute changes to the choir's jubilee performance disappoint Simon. A therapy session leads to big revelations for Wilhelm.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Secrets come to light as an unexpected renegade spoils Simon's plan. Wilhelm's fateful speech approaches — will he rise to the occasion?

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: A winter break has passed and Prince Wilhelm and the rest of his classmates are back at Hillerska. When Wilhelm tries to take revenge on August, and win back Simon's trust, he creates problems that threaten the entire monarchy.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Wilhelm's speech has consequences not only in the court but also throughout the school. The prince and Simon are determined to enjoy their relationship.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: School restrictions and court politics put a strain on Wilhelm and Simon. August's attempt to make amends goes unacknowledged. The gang goes camping.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Wilhelm sees the throne looming on the horizon. Sara contemplates returning to Hillerska. The online harassment of Simon follows him home.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: August and Vincent organize a strike action that exposes the differences between Wilhelm and Simon. Felice and Sara can no longer avoid each other.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Wilhelm confronts his past and future at his lavish birthday ceremony. August finds hope in the arms of Sara. In the palace, Simon makes a decision.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: With Hillerska's fate hanging in the balance, Wilhelm and Simon weigh duty against love as they discover what it takes to truly follow their hearts.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: The prince and Simon are determined to be together, but what are they willing to sacrifice when realizing that their freedom and love might be at odds with the Royal ideals, traditions, and responsibilities?
